*''Italian Narrative Poetry'', 1824
*''Daponte's Observations'', 1825
*''Scottish Song'', 1826
*''Novel-Writing'', 1827
*''Moli<U+00E8>re'', 1828
*''Irving's Granada'', 1829
*''Asylum for the Blind'', 1830
*''Poetry and Romance of the Italians'', 1831
*''Cervantes'', 1837
