*''Bancroft's United States'', 1841
*''Madame Calderon's Mexico'', 1843
*''Ticknor's Spanish Literature'', 1850<ref>In editions after 1855 only.</ref>
The following were omitted:
*''English Literature of the Nineteenth Century'', 1832
*''Kenyon's poems'', 1839
*''Chateaubriand'', 1839
*''Mariotti's Italy'', 1842

